<td><FONT SIZE="1" FACE="Verdana, Arial" COLOR="#2f2f4f">Originally posted by Nazrin Wraithforge on 04-04-2001 10:08 AM<BR></FONT>
<TEXTAREA NAME="EditedMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">Ok my general opinion here is that this is
a very contested spawn and we all know that Verant needs to do something about it. Aside from that in Scenario A although I do not like the idea of alternatives camping I would expect them to keep the FG's killed so the path to Ragefire is clear.
Scenerio B is a hard one but I would at least give them about 1/2 hr - 1 hour to organise a crew too dispatch Ragefire organising a crew too kill him is hard for many clerics that are independent of not part of an uber guild.

As a whole the problem here is really that Uber guilds in my believe are Farming these too there twink clerics as majority of their main clerics already have them.  This causes issues as Clerics that are ready too do Ragefire can't because of Farmers.  In my personal believe is a guild has its first cleric ready for Ragefire the Uber guilds should help that cleric get the Item as it will benefit not just possibly their guild should he decide to join them on raids but also his own guild.  Independant clerics are in a similiar boat.

My biggest Suggestion is that Uber guild should stop Farming for Twinks I personally know two guilds on Tunare that are doing this which will go unamed.</TEXTAREA>
